From 8a4ba789ca015741818d2f66c39d286e7d87f3c1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 21 Jun 2026 23:13:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] fix: resolve remaining audit defects (Phase 3, round 2)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Fixes 9 more confirmed UX/logic defects from the feature audit:
- CHAT-06: dim + 'Uploading…' label for pending attachment previews
- CHAT-07: inline 'Saving…' indicator in the message editor
- NAV-08: bulk-delete error now names which chats failed and why
- AGT-12: clearer network/HTTP error messages in fetchAgentTemplates
- AGT-02: comment explaining why action tags are excluded from filters
- CAT-05: one-time toast when artist filter falls back to full catalog
- FAN-04: always-visible username/follower caption on touch devices
- FARC-01: BaseBuilder address configurable via env (default unchanged)
- ART-04: lenient http(s) URL validation for artist streaming/social fields

Investigated and confirmed as false positives (no change): NAV-06 (list not
virtualized), CONN-02 (page already filters to ALLOWED_CONNECTORS), NAV-11
(query key already changes on org switch), AGT-05 (removals applied before submit).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
